  • Method Details

    • init

      @PostConstruct public void init()
      Initialize the dtos. Create the objects for:
      • the revision upload pdf
      • The submission this page is about
      • the scientific forum this paper was submitted into
      • the list of co-authors for this submission
      • the pagination for papers
      • the pagination for reviews
      • the reviewed by object
      • the newest paper in the submission
      No data can be loaded form the datasource at this point. (See the onLoad() method).

    • onLoad

      public void onLoad()
      Get the correct submission id from the view param (will be called in a view action) and load all data that should be displayed from the datasource:
      • The submission this page is about
      • the scientific forum this submission was submitted into
      • the list of co-authors for this submission
      • the pagination for papers
      • the pagination for reviews
      • the reviewed by object
      • the newest paper in the submission
      Throws:
      IllegalAccessException - If the user has no access rights for this submission
